node.text: The reason I work so hard on building different streams of income, a long-standing brand, and building a legacy — it’s so my baby girl can have endless opportunities as she gets older. Society, a country, or a government doesn’t define how successful you’ll be — your daily actions will 🙏🏼🚀

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by PR & Branding Expert 🇺🇸🇻🇪 on September 05, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Billionaires lose millions to become billionaires. Millionaires lose thousands to become millionaires. Broke people want to lose nothing to become rich.'.

node.text: You gotta spend money to make money — Nothing beats investing in yourself! 🚀💰
